<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/18051373-jane-goldberg"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1362436408i/18051373._UX100_CR0,13,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/18051373-jane-goldberg">Jane Goldberg</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Nothing. They just have Special Agent Pendergast as the main character. Still Life is much different. Not supernatural. Just a guy who was...can&apos;t say<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Nothing. They just have Special Agent Pendergast as the main character. Still Life is much different. Not supernatural. Just a guy who was...can't say. I love this character. I'd love to meet him. He is so refined, but breaks out of his character in Still Life when he befriends an 18 yr old female who can't stay out of trouble. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
