        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer221030022" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2789427571000647049">The Diogenes cycle with the Pendergast series is my favorite section. This one takes place in Italy. And true to its name has religious connotations. Not my favorite of the three, but still quite a baffling mystery to the very end.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


